      <title>美光为何发布如此疲弱的预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/why-micron-posted-such-a-weak-forecast-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[New Street Research 全球技术基础设施主管 Pierre Ferragu 详细分析了美光的盈利报告和收入预测。美光的收入预测比预期低约 10 亿美元，随后股价在尾盘交易中暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/why-micron-posted-such-a-weak-forecast-video</guid>
